casebody.data:
No. 10-1027. Missouri Title Loans, Inc., Petitioner v. Beverly Brewer. 563 U.S. 971, 131 S. Ct. 2875,

179 L. Ed. 2d 1184,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 3378. May 2, 2011.

Petition for writ of certio-rari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the Supreme Court of Missouri for further consideration in light of AT&T Mobility LLC v. Concepcion, 563 U.S. 333, 131 S. Ct. 1740, 179 L. Ed. 2d 742 (2011).
